      "type": "text",
      "id": "insight_text",
      "x": 515,
      "y": 466,
      "width": 575,
      "height": 88,
      "text": "Key: queryLoop() is a while(true) with transition state.\nState.transition records WHY we continued:\n  tool_use | budget_continuation | max_output_tokens_recovery\nThis makes recovery paths testable without inspecting message content.",
