      "x": 515,
      "y": 586,
      "width": 575,
      "height": 118,
      "text": "Execution side (src/query.ts):\n\n  +-- Tool dispatch --> routes by tool name\n  +-- Concurrent tools: Promise.all for independent calls\n  +-- Speculative: start before user confirms\n  +-- Results wrapped as tool_result content blocks\n  +-- Errors captured, retried w/ backoff\n\nToken budget checked each iteration (tokenBudget.ts)",
      "originalText": "Execution side (src/query.ts):\n\n  +-- Tool dispatch --> routes by tool name\n  +-- Concurrent tools: Promise.all for independent calls\n  +-- Speculative: start before user confirms\n  +-- Results wrapped as tool_result content blocks\n  +-- Errors captured, retried w/ backoff\n\nToken budget checked each iteration (tokenBudget.ts)",
